description: The development of the Sustainable Management Plan for Vaitele, Apia, Samoa

subproject.corporate outcome: Strengthened capacities of national human rights institutions
subproject.description:
1. Working with the Vaitele Community to formulate a SMP.
2. Increased knowledge and awareness of land use planning.
3. Enh Develope SMP and pass in to legislative under the PUMA Act. 
4. Enhanced technical and systemic capacities for land use planning.
